Lyric:
[by:农田师]
[ar:Peter Hollens]
[ti:Skyrim]
[00:29.62]Dovakhiin, Dovakhiin, naal ok zin los vahriin
[00:33.18]Wah dein vokul mahfoerook asht vaal!
[00:36.78]Ahrk fin norok paal graan fod nust hon zindro zaan,
[00:40.66]Dovakhiin, fah hin kogaan mu draal!
[00:58.62]Huzrah nu, kul do od, wah aan bok lingrah vod,
[01:05.62]Ahrk fin tey, boziik fun, do fin gein!
[01:20.07]Wo lost fran wah ney dov, ahrk fin reyliik do jul,
[01:27.17]Voth aan suleyk wah ronit faal krein!
[01:34.10]Ahrk fin Kel lost prodah, do ved viing ko fin krah,
[01:37.80]Tol fod zeymah win kein meyz fundein!
[01:41.15]Alduin, feyn do jun, kruziik vokun staadnau,
[01:44.85]Voth aan bahlok wah diivon fin lein!
[02:02.50]FUS RO DAH!(dragon shout)fent alok, fod fin vul dovah nok,
[02:09.60]Fen kos nahlot mahfaeraak ahrk ruz!
[02:16.82]Paaz Keizaal fen kos stin no bein Alduin jot.
[02:24.35]FUS RO DAH! fent alok, fod fin vul dovah nok,
[02:31.10]Fen kos nahlot mahfaeraak ahrk ruz!
[02:38.30]FUS RO DAH
[02:39.45]Dovakhiin, naal ok zin los vahriin
[02:42.10]Wah dein vokul mahfoerook asht vaal!
[02:45.65]Ahrk fin norok paal graan fod nust hon zindro zaan,
[02:49.40]Dovakhiin, fah hin kogaan mu draal!
